tests.title: Create Blipp Builder(Classic) Version and plist
tests.fullTitle: BLIPP Creation Tests in a Project - BESPOKE, BBCLASSIC version, plist, BBNEW(Designer) with marker and BLIPP API jsversion, publish - country IN Create Blipp Builder(Classic) Version and plist
tests.code:
logger.info("Creating Blipp Builder(Classic) Version >> "+bbclassicid());
supportapi.createversion(bRole, bbclassicid(), 'builder_v2', ' ', function(resp){
// logger.info("Blipp Version created and response is>>>"+resp);
var vid = JSON.parse(resp);
global.bbclasssverid = function(){ return vid.Id};
logger.info("Creating plist for BB Classic having versionid> "+bbclasssverid());
supportapi.createplist(bRole, bbclassicid(), bbclasssverid(), function(presp){
expect(presp).to.contain("MD5", "BlippHash");
var plistresp = JSON.parse(presp);
global.plistid = function(){ return plistresp.Id; };
expect(plistid()).to.not.be.undefined;
expect(plistid()).to.be.a('Number');
done();
});
});

tests.title: SEARCHING a project
tests.fullTitle: BLIPP Creation Tests in a Project - BESPOKE, BBCLASSIC version, plist, BBNEW(Designer) with marker and BLIPP API jsversion, publish - country IN SEARCHING a project
tests.code:
logger.info("Searching a project named> "+searchprojName()+" with id>"+searchprojid());
const allprojs = '/campaigns?orderby=created_at__desc&limit=1000';
supportapi.fetcher(bRole, allprojs, function(allproj){
var projects = JSON.parse(allproj);
projects.map(function(project){
if(project.Name.toLowerCase() == searchprojName().toLowerCase() && project.Deleted == 0)
global.foundproj = function(){ return project.Id; };
});
expect(foundproj()).to.equal(searchprojid());
done();
});

tests.title: UPDATE CAMPAIGN
tests.fullTitle: BLIPP Creation Tests in a Project - BESPOKE, BBCLASSIC version, plist, BBNEW(Designer) with marker and BLIPP API jsversion, publish - country IN UPDATE CAMPAIGN
tests.code:
global.createdprojName = function(){ return "APIProj_"+now.getTime(); };
global.createddesc = function() { return "Test Proj created from API"; };
var udpateprojbody = { "Name": createdprojName(), "Description":createddesc() }
supportapi.creator(bRole,'/group/7677/campaign', udpateprojbody, function(uproj) {
var upid = JSON.parse(uproj);
global.updateprojid = function(){ return upid.Id; };
logger.info("Proj to be modified Created and id is >> "+updateprojid());
global.updatedprojname = function(){ return "UDATEDapiproj_"+now.getTime(); };
global.updateddesc = function() { return "UPDATING from api"; };
var ubody = { 'Name':updatedprojname(), 'Description':updateddesc() }
var uapi ='/campaign/'+updateprojid();
logger.info("Ubody used for update> "+JSON.stringify(ubody));
supportapi.updater(bRole,uapi, ubody, function(text) {
//logger.info('Updated Successfully > '+text); // Validate response with updated values
expect(text).to.contain(updatedprojname(),updateddesc());
done();
});
});

tests.title: Fetch Blipps in a Proj and DELETEBLIPP
tests.fullTitle: BLIPP Creation Tests in a Project - BESPOKE, BBCLASSIC version, plist, BBNEW(Designer) with marker and BLIPP API jsversion, publish - country IN Fetch Blipps in a Proj and DELETEBLIPP
tests.code:
logger.info("Fetching Blipps of project id>"+projid());
supportapi.fetchprojblipps(bRole, projid(), function(resp) {
// console.log(" PROJBLIPPS Response>> "+blippresp);
var blippresp = JSON.parse(resp);
var blippsgot = blippresp.map(function(blippresp){
if(delblipp.toLowerCase() == blippresp.Name.toLowerCase() && blippresp.Status != "DELETED" && delblippid() == blippresp.Id )
global.delblippfound = function(){ return blippresp.Id };
});
logger.info("BLIPP_TO_BE_DELETED found > "+delblippfound());
var delblipapi = '/blipp/'+delblippfound();
supportapi.remover(bRole, delblipapi, function(resp){
logger.info(delblipp+"DELETED Successfully..."+resp);
expect(resp).to.contain("OK");
done();
});
});

});
});

done();
});
});

logger.info("Creating Blipp Builder(Classic) Version >> "+bbclassicid());
supportapi.createversion(bRole, bbclassicid(), 'builder_v2', ' ', function(resp){
// logger.info("Blipp Version created and response is>>>"+resp);
var vid = JSON.parse(resp);
global.bbclasssverid = function(){ return vid.Id};
logger.info("Creating plist for BB Classic having versionid> "+bbclasssverid());
supportapi.createplist(bRole, bbclassicid(), bbclasssverid(), function(presp){

global.plistid = function(){ return plistresp.Id; };
expect(plistid()).to.not.be.undefined;
expect(plistid()).to.be.a('Number');
done();
});
});

logger.info("Searching a project named> "+searchprojName()+" with id>"+searchprojid());
const allprojs = '/campaigns?orderby=created_at__desc&limit=1000';
supportapi.fetcher(bRole, allprojs, function(allproj){
var projects = JSON.parse(allproj);
projects.map(function(project){
if(project.Name.toLowerCase() == searchprojName().toLowerCase() && project.Deleted == 0)
global.foundproj = function(){ return project.Id; };
});
expect(foundproj()).to.equal(searchprojid());
done();
});

global.createdprojName = function(){ return "APIProj_"+now.getTime(); };
global.createddesc = function() { return "Test Proj created from API"; };
var udpateprojbody = { "Name": createdprojName(), "Description":createddesc() }
supportapi.creator(bRole,'/group/7677/campaign', udpateprojbody, function(uproj) {
var upid = JSON.parse(uproj);
global.updateprojid = function(){ return upid.Id; };
logger.info("Proj to be modified Created and id is >> "+updateprojid());
global.updatedprojname = function(){ return "UDATEDapiproj_"+now.getTime(); };
global.updateddesc = function() { return "UPDATING from api"; };
var ubody = { 'Name':updatedprojname(), 'Description':updateddesc() }
var uapi ='/campaign/'+updateprojid();
logger.info("Ubody used for update> "+JSON.stringify(ubody));
supportapi.updater(bRole,uapi, ubody, function(text) {
//logger.info('Updated Successfully > '+text); // Validate response with updated values
expect(text).to.contain(updatedprojname(),updateddesc());
done();
});
});

passes.code:
logger.info("Fetching Blipps of project id>"+projid());
supportapi.fetchprojblipps(bRole, projid(), function(resp) {
// console.log(" PROJBLIPPS Response>> "+blippresp);
var blippresp = JSON.parse(resp);
var blippsgot = blippresp.map(function(blippresp){
if(delblipp.toLowerCase() == blippresp.Name.toLowerCase() && blippresp.Status != "DELETED" && delblippid() == blippresp.Id )
global.delblippfound = function(){ return blippresp.Id };
});
logger.info("BLIPP_TO_BE_DELETED found > "+delblippfound());
var delblipapi = '/blipp/'+delblippfound();
supportapi.remover(bRole, delblipapi, function(resp){
logger.info(delblipp+"DELETED Successfully..."+resp);
expect(resp).to.contain("OK");
done();
});
});

passes.fullTitle: BLIPP Creation Tests in a Project - BESPOKE, BBCLASSIC version, plist, BBNEW(Designer) with marker and BLIPP API jsversion, publish - country IN Fetch Blipps in a Proj and DELETEBLIPP
passes.code:
logger.info("Fetching Blipps of project id>"+projid());
supportapi.fetchprojblipps(bRole, projid(), function(resp) {
// console.log(" PROJBLIPPS Response>> "+blippresp);
var blippresp = JSON.parse(resp);
var blippsgot = blippresp.map(function(blippresp){
if(delblipp.toLowerCase() == blippresp.Name.toLowerCase() && blippresp.Status != "DELETED" && delblippid() == blippresp.Id )
global.delblippfound = function(){ return blippresp.Id };
});
logger.info("BLIPP_TO_BE_DELETED found > "+delblippfound());
var delblipapi = '/blipp/'+delblippfound();
supportapi.remover(bRole, delblipapi, function(resp){
logger.info(delblipp+"DELETED Successfully..."+resp);
expect(resp).to.contain("OK");
done();
});
});
